		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>After battering your target with a vicious spell, you follow up with yet another assault, drawing on your reserves of remaining energy.</em></p><p><strong>Bonus Action</strong> - 1 Creature - 1/Short Rest - Magical</p><p>You can use this ability after damaging a creature with a spell of 1st level or higher. You choose one target that took damage from your spell.</p><p><strong>Dexterity Save</strong> </p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes damage equal to 4d10 + your intelligence modifier. The damage type can be &amp;reference[acid], &amp;reference[cold], &amp;reference[lightning], &amp;reference[fire], or &amp;reference[thunder].</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage.</p></li></ul>",
